{"tid":1252812,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男友扑嘢時碌IG，咁代表咩","createTime":"2019-06-23T08:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T14:01:20.000Z","uid":57261,"like":34,"dislike":810,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"5ba47704fd12a9a51866ee4efd569f09e92ac40c","tid":1252812,"uid":57261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"早兩日同男友喺屋企扑嘢 女上完佢一個翻身<br />\n係我期待咗好耐嘅男上 插插下佢突然拎部手機出嚟<br />\n原來喺度碌IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我嗰下見佢咁氣定神閒 就問佢做咩係度玩手機<br />\n點知佢話 無吖得閒望下咋嘛<br />\n我嗰下即刻灰咗 究竟佢一路抽插我 一路碌手機係咩意思<br />\n<br />\n利申 藍絲<br />\n<br />\n正評: 小事啦 屙屎都會撳手機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負評: 問問問 嫌你鬆呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86920e01e6df481f19c602cd29aa049c6844ba3b","tid":1252812,"uid":164920,"like":441,"dislike":3,"score":438,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:17:09.000Z","msg":"藍絲就去撐警大遊行啦，仲扑野。國家需要你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231715b80e27014e4bed10b899527de271a6785f","tid":1252812,"uid":164608,"like":125,"dislike":0,"score":125,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:19:05.000Z","msg":"對住你射唔出咪睇J圖囉"},{"pid":"c0d0d45cae2794c32e5d3e33da4fe865e5562fad","tid":1252812,"uid":245553,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:20:34.000Z","msg":"睇下其他女先勁d"},{"pid":"f1da2526024564a8fc5cfafb1d1568796740a20a","tid":1252812,"uid":88428,"like":161,"dislike":0,"score":161,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:20:43.000Z","msg":"你一路女上一路食飯盒囉"},{"pid":"9590b4c47be17984c5c218285cb4769f7d8c32c2","tid":1252812,"uid":58852,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:22:45.000Z